{"title":"朋友，在北京…………","authors":["顾工"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":8,"day":30}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"朋友，在北京…………"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顾工"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从中南海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从石狮子旁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走出来几个黑人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"气概轩昂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼睛闪射着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳的光；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"内心蕴藏着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火山的岩浆！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚步更坚定，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像铁锤敲在铁砧上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们走向"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战斗的山岗……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金发的友人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拿着彩笔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正描绘着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京的屋宇………"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涂抹赤红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"点染新绿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她整个的心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跳动在画里！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带着这画，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘洋过海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无论挂到那儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都会引起一片惊喜……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红星"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她接受"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一颗红五星，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"珍爱地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别在衣襟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她感到世界"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更加芳馨；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她感到自己"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骤然年青。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"微笑、微笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们更可亲；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她那碧蓝的眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"变得更晶莹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"划"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北海的水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在激荡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"游船上动摇着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肤色不同的臂膀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马埃斯特腊山的人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刚果河旁的人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长江流域的人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一齐起落着桨……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑声，鸽铃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"融成歌唱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们奋力划向"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪光的地方……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}